	<ThingDef ParentName="ApparelBase">
		<defName>Apparel_HelmetLegacyEliteMeh</defName>
		<label>"Legacy" helmet</label>
		<description>"Legacy" ("Legacy") - this decorative-looking helmet is actually an ancient development of the best minds of the "Mechalit" faction - nowadays an irreproducible technology. This helmet was designed for the deserved high commanders of the faction, it not only emphasizes the status of the owner, but also protects him well. The built-in neural network shows the target's vulnerabilities and all trajectories of movement, greatly helping the owner both in close combat and in long-range combat. But the main feature of this helmet is its "" invulnerability. "The lost technology of mechanite regeneration instantly restores any damage to the helmet, and over time the helmet does not wear out. Fathers pass it on to their children, and those to their children, which is why the helmet got this name. This helmet cannot be bought. or crafted on the machine in the usual way. With the included Royalty add-on, the helmet improves the psi characteristics of the wearer and is suitable for nobility by the title of Count "inclusive. The same armor of the "Mechalit" and "Mechalit Renegades" factions does not differ in characteristics, but only has a different color corresponding to the faction.</description>
		<techLevel>Spacer</techLevel>
		<graphicData>
			<texPath>head-HelmetLegacy/HelmetLegacyQ</texPath>
			<graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
		</graphicData>
		<statBases>
